title: Darryl Dawkins dies at 58; ferocious dunker altered game of basketball
text:
Published By: Baltimore Sun: NBA - Today 
Darryl Dawkins, whose ferocious style of dunking the basketball changed the rules of the game and paved the way for breakaway rims, has died...
